                  </persName>
            . I am shopman to Mr. Sizer.<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="181201150041"></xptr>About six o'clock on the 4th of January the witness France stepped his foot on the door, he said, here are two men that have cut your window, if you will go with me we will secure them. The window was knocked completely out, nothing was removed that we could see.</p>
